==English==
===Etymology===
a [[portmanteau]] of [[over]] (with respect to available funds) and [[draft]] (in the sense of a request for funds).
===Noun===
'''overdraft'''
# the act of [[overdraw]]ing a [[bank account]]
# the [[amount]] [[overdrawn]]
# the [[maximum]] amount allowed to be overdrawn
